自2001年，默勒一直参与包括[[维基百科|维基百科]]在内[[维基媒体基金会|维基媒体基金会]]项目，他不仅是一名编者，还是[[MediaWiki|MediaWiki]]软件和[[维基新闻|维基新闻]]的开发者<ref>{{cite news|title=Wikinews trumpets online revolution|url=http://www.journalism.co.uk/news/story1178.shtml|publisher=Mousetrap Media Ltd|work=Online Journalism News|first=Jemina|last=Kiss|date=2004-12-15|accessdate=2008-05-13|archive-date=2008-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202193019/http://www.journalism.co.uk/news/story1178.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他利用用户名Eloquence起草了维基新闻的初版提案<ref name="weiss0210"/><ref>{{cite book  | last =Allan  | first =Stuart   | title =Online news: journalism and the Internet  | publisher =McGraw-Hill International  | year =2006  | pages =136 | isbn = 0-335-22121-1}}</ref>，还在[[维基共享资源|维基共享资源]]的开发中起到重要作用<ref name="donohue">{{cite web|url=http://www.brandrepublic.com/News/775852/Wikimedia-hires-Moeller-deputy-director/|title=Wikimedia hires Moeller as deputy director|work=Brand Republic News|publisher=Brand Republic|accessdate=2008-05-13|date=2008-01-10|last=Donohue|first=Alex|archive-date=2012-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406102912/http://www.brandrepublic.com/News/775852/Wikimedia-hires-Moeller-deputy-director/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。穆勒于2004年3月率先提出了维基共享资源的理念<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/wikipedia-l/2004-March/014885.html|work=[Wikipedia-l]|title=Proposal: commons.wikimedia.org|publisher=Wikimedia Foundation|accessdate=2008-05-13|date=2004-03-19|last=Möller|first=Erik|archive-date=2013-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131209124611/http://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/wikipedia-l/2004-March/014885.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，他描述出维基百科和维基新闻与《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》之间的差异，表示：“维基新闻的条目的时效性很短，所以能为促成永久持续下去的知识提供基础<ref name="weiss0210" />。”默勒在2005年首尔公民记者论坛上表示：“我们是新媒体，我们制定属于我们的规则<ref name="kiss0714" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ohmynews.com/articleview/article_view.asp?no=236662&rel_no=1|title=Citizen Reporters Turn to Print for Delivery|work=OhmyNews International|publisher=english.ohmynews.com|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2005-07-11|last=Pollard|first=William|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605042855/http://english.ohmynews.com/articleview/article_view.asp?no=236662&rel_no=1|archivedate=2011-06-05}}</ref>。”他表示，维基新闻每日出版打印版，还在增加其它格式，包括文章的音频版<ref name="kiss0714">{{cite web|url=http://www.journalism.co.uk/2/articles/51449.php|work=Journalism.co.uk - Online Journalism News|title=News round-up: Citizen journalism is officially cool|publisher=Mousetrap Media Ltd|accessdate=2008-05-13|date=2005-07-14|last=Kiss|first=Jemima|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071118145510/http://www.journalism.co.uk/2/articles/51449.php|archivedate=2007-11-18}}</ref>。默勒因2005年[[伦敦七七爆炸案|伦敦七七爆炸案]]期间维基新闻的访问流量增加八倍，以及其对新闻自由的影响，受到Journalism.co.uk的采访<ref name="kiss0713">{{cite web|url=http://www.journalism.co.uk/2/articles/51443.php|work=Journalism.co.uk - Online Journalism News|title=Wikinews supercharged by London bombings coverage|publisher=Mousetrap Media Ltd|accessdate=2008-05-13|date=2005-07-13|last=Kiss|first=Jemima|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071109103516/http://www.journalism.co.uk/2/articles/51443.php|archivedate=2007-11-09}}</ref>。“尽管维基新闻比维基百科要小得多，但它在报道新闻方面的潜力远远超出了维基百科现在正在做的事情。“默勒表示<ref name="kiss0713" />。他在维基新闻定期给出“State of the Wiki”报道，为项目使用出自其他媒体来源的原始素材和整合信息辩护<ref>{{cite book | last =Kolodzy | first =Janet  | title =Convergence Journalism: Writing and Reporting Across the News Media | url =https://archive.org/details/convergencejourn0000kolo | publisher =Rowman & Littlefield | year =2006 | pages =[https://archive.org/details/convergencejourn0000kolo/page/238 238]–239, 243 | isbn = 0-7425-3886-9}}</ref>。

2005年6月，默勒被任命为维基媒体基金会的首席研究员，但由于个人与董事会成员存在分歧，于同年8月辞去该职<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/foundation-l/2005-August/017269.html|work=[Foundation-l]|title=Resignation as CRO|publisher=[[Wikimedia_Foundation|Wikimedia Foundation]]|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2005-08-17|last=Möller|first=Erik|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810161019/https://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/foundation-l/2005-August/017269.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name='Meta Wiki CRO'>{{cite web 
 |url=http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Chief_Research_Officer 
 |title=Chief Research Officer 
 |accessdate=2008-05-13 
 |publisher=Wikimedia Foundation 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070128064835/http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Chief_Research_Officer 
 |archivedate=2007-01-28 
 |deadurl=yes 
 }}</ref>。他曾担任总部设在荷兰<ref name="donohue" />的[[OmegaWiki|OmegaWiki]][[非营利组织|非营利]]法律机构Stichting Open Progress的首席技术官<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/c/a/2008/01/20/BUCGUHQ5F.DTL&type=printable|title=Bay Area Biz: Movers and shakers|work=San Francisco Chronicle|publisher=www.sfgate.com|accessdate=2008-05-13|date=2008-01-20|last=Staff|archive-date=2008-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080124101936/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2008%2F01%2F20%2FBUCGUHQ5F.DTL&type=printable|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在Stichting Open Progress，默勒担任致力于Omegawiki运营的开发小组总管<ref name="donohue" />。默勒还开办了WikiEducator.org等其他wiki社群<ref name="donohue" />。

2006年9月，默勒入选维基媒体基金会董事会，接替[[安吉拉·比斯利|安吉拉·比斯利]]的职位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heise.de/tp/r4/artikel/24/24476/1.html|title=TP: Die neuen Herausforderungen der Wikipedia|work=Telepolis|publisher=www.heise.de|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2007-01-20|last=Kleinz|first=Torsten|language=de|archive-date=2009-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129171339/http://www.heise.de/tp/r4/artikel/24/24476/1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Resolution:Replacement_Board_member_2006|title=Resolution:Replacement Board member 2006 - Wikimedia Foundation|publisher=Wikimedia Foundation|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2006-09-26|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326085418/https://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Resolution:Replacement_Board_member_2006|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年10月，默勒担任行政秘书<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heise.de/newsticker/Wechsel-an-der-Wikimedia-Spitze--/meldung/80171/from/rss09|work=heise online|title= Wechsel an der Wikimedia-Spitze|publisher=www.heise.de|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2006-10-28|language=de}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://idgnow.uol.com.br/carreira/2006/11/06/idgnoticia.2006-11-06.7717485194/|title=Jimmy Wales sai da presidência da enciclopédia online Wikipedia|work=Carreira - IDG Now!|publisher=idgnow.uol.com.br|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2006-11-06|language=pt|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706161122/http://idgnow.uol.com.br/carreira/2006/11/06/idgnoticia.2006-11-06.7717485194/|archivedate=2011-07-06}}</ref>。默勒2007年12月从董事会辞职，被提拔为副董事<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/foundation-l/2007-December/036323.html|title=Announcing Erik Moeller as Wikimedia Deputy Director|work=[Foundation-l]|publisher=Wikimedia Foundation|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2007-12-18|last=Sue Gardner|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102033326/https://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/foundation-l/2007-December/036323.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年10月，他被正式任命为维基媒体基金会的副董事，该职位于2008年10月生效<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Erik_M%C3%B6ller_Deputy_Director|title=Erik Möller Deputy Director - Wikimedia Foundation|publisher=Wikimedia Foundation|accessdate=2008-05-12|date=2008-01-09|archive-date=2008-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080515190315/http://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Erik_M%C3%B6ller_Deputy_Director|dead-url=no}}</ref>。作为副董事，默勒参与维基媒体基金会的融资分析，并与执行董事[[苏·加德纳|苏·加德纳]]向[[太阳计算机系统|太阳计算机系统]]公司作展示，为维基媒体基金会公司赢得资金<ref name="zwei">{{cite web|url=http://heise.de/newsticker/meldung/Zwei-Millionen-US-Dollar-fuer-Wikipedia-Co-176802.html|title=Zwei Millionen US-Dollar für Wikipedia & Co|work=heise online|publisher=Heise Zeitschriften Verlag|accessdate=2010-05-15|date=2008-01-09|language=de|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926025416/https://www.heise.de/newsticker/meldung/Zwei-Millionen-US-Dollar-fuer-Wikipedia-Co-176802.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本次演示后来被维基新闻泄露出去<ref name="zwei" />。

担任维基媒体基金会副董事的默勒负责组织的管理和执行技术策略<ref name="donohue" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/blogs/bayareabiz/month?blogid=44&year=2008&month=01&cat=&o=10|title=Bay Area Biz : January 2008|work=San Francisco Chronicle|publisher=www.sfgate.com|accessdate=2008-05-13|date=2008-01-13|last=Staff}}</ref>。默勒向《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》解释道，基金会在对待各种交易时需要很小心，表示：“我们不希望进入会与目标产生冲突的交易中<ref>{{cite news  | url =http://seattletimes.com/html/businesstechnology/2004286879_btwikipedia17.html  | last =Semuels  | first =Alana  | title =Wikipedia Experiences Growing Pains  | work =[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]  | page =Financial section  | date =2008-03-13  | accessdate =2015-07-16  | archive-date =2014-08-13  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140813173456/http://seattletimes.com/html/businesstechnology/2004286879_btwikipedia17.html  | dead-url =no  }}</ref>。”默勒是维基媒体基金会驻[[网络生命大百科|网络生命大百科]]这一理事会机构的代表<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eol.org/info/3?language=en#COUNCIL|title=Institutional Partners|work=Encyclopedia of Life|publisher=www.eol.org|accessdate=2014-06-04|archive-date=2017-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728041058/http://eol.org/info/3?language=en#COUNCIL|dead-url=no}}</ref>。透过这次接触，默勒说服[[艾尔弗·斯隆基金|阿尔弗雷德·斯隆基金会]]（{{lang|en|Alfred P.Sloan Foundation}}，网络生命大百科的支持者）向维基媒体基金会捐赠300万美元，这也是基金会迄今为止所收到的单笔最大数额的捐赠<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/foundation-l/2008-March/040440.html|title=Sloan awards Wikimedia USD 1m annually for three years|work=[Foundation-l]|publisher=Wikimedia Foundation|accessdate=2008-05-15|date=2008-03-25|last=Sue Gardner|archive-date=2020-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326101535/https://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/foundation-l/2008-March/040440.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，默勒的[[德文维基百科|德文维基百科]]账号被封禁，因为他创建、实施并使用了 "超级保护 "权（即德文維基百科管理員也無法編輯，只有基金會帳號能編輯），推翻了[[德文维基百科|德文维基百科]]社群先前達成的在法律和技术问题解决之前不启用新的图片浏览机制的决定<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heise.de/newsticker/meldung/Superprotect-Wikimedia-behaelt-das-letzte-Wort-bei-Wikipedia-2290569.html|title="Superprotect": Wikimedia behält das letzte Wort bei Wikipedia|author=Torsten Kleinz|date=2014-08-12|work=heise online|accessdate=2015-07-16|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209045641/https://www.heise.de/newsticker/meldung/Superprotect-Wikimedia-behaelt-das-letzte-Wort-bei-Wikipedia-2290569.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/08/18/class_war_wikipedias_workers_revolt_after_bourgeois_papershufflers_suspend_democracy/|title=Class war! Wikipedia's workers revolt again|publisher=|accessdate=2015-07-16|archive-date=2017-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728072845/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/08/18/class_war_wikipedias_workers_revolt_after_bourgeois_papershufflers_suspend_democracy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年4月30日，默勒离开基金会<ref>{{cite web|title=Management changes continue: Erik Möller to leave Foundation|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Wikipedia_Signpost/2015-04-15/News_and_notes|publisher=Wikipedia Signpost|accessdate=2015-04-19|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018182239/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Wikipedia_Signpost/2015-04-15/News_and_notes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
